<table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>
	<tr>
		<td valign=middle align=left width=22><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=1 width=20 border=0></td>
		
    <td valign=middle align=right class="header">Searching Messages</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr>
    <td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">To search for any particular 
      message in the Inbox or in the other folders. Follow the steps below:</td>
  </tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr>
    <td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Search Message Using 
      A Keyword</td>
  </tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Messaging</strong> 
      link from the main menu to view the messages in the Inbox.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">To search for a message using a keyword, 
      type the keyword in the search field, select which folder to search in and 
      filter the search with the <em>All Messages</em>, <em>Unread</em>, or <em>Read</em> 
      options.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Next, click on the <strong>Show</strong> 
      button to list out the searched results. (It will search any subject that 
      matches the keyword)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Search Message By Folders</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Messaging</strong> 
      link from the main menu to view the messages in the Inbox.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Select which folder to search in and 
      filter the search with the All Messages, Unread, or Read options.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		
    <td valign=top align=left class="text">Next, click on the <strong>Show</strong> 
      button to list out all the messages under the folder.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
